31uint16_t
32dst_region_computeid(const isc_region_t *source) {
33 uint32_t ac;
34 const unsigned char *p;
35 int size;
36
37 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
38 REQUIRE(source->length >= 4);
39
40 p = source->base;
41 size = source->length;
42
43 for (ac = 0; size > 1; size -= 2, p += 2)
44 ac += ((*p) << 8) + *(p + 1);
45
46 if (size > 0)
47 ac += ((*p) << 8);
48 ac += (ac >> 16) & 0xffff;
49
50 return ((uint16_t)(ac & 0xffff));
51}
52
53uint16_t
54dst_region_computerid(const isc_region_t *source) {
55 uint32_t ac;
56 const unsigned char *p;
57 int size;
58
59 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
60 REQUIRE(source->length >= 4);
61
62 p = source->base;
63 size = source->length;
64
65 ac = ((*p) << 8) + *(p + 1);
66 ac |= DNS_KEYFLAG_REVOKE;
67 for (size -= 2, p +=2; size > 1; size -= 2, p += 2)
68 ac += ((*p) << 8) + *(p + 1);
69
70 if (size > 0)
71 ac += ((*p) << 8);
72 ac += (ac >> 16) & 0xffff;
73
74 return ((uint16_t)(ac & 0xffff));
75}

125bool
126dst_key_iszonekey(const dst_key_t *key) {
127 REQUIRE(VALID_KEY(key));
128
129 if ((key->key_flags & DNS_KEYTYPE_NOAUTH) != 0)
130 return (false);
131 if ((key->key_flags & DNS_KEYFLAG_OWNERMASK) != DNS_KEYOWNER_ZONE)
132 return (false);
133 if (key->key_proto != DNS_KEYPROTO_DNSSEC &&
134 key->key_proto != DNS_KEYPROTO_ANY)
135 return (false);
136 return (true);
137}
138
139bool
140dst_key_isnullkey(const dst_key_t *key) {
141 REQUIRE(VALID_KEY(key));
142
143 if ((key->key_flags & DNS_KEYFLAG_TYPEMASK) != DNS_KEYTYPE_NOKEY)
144 return (false);
145 if ((key->key_flags & DNS_KEYFLAG_OWNERMASK) != DNS_KEYOWNER_ZONE)
146 return (false);
147 if (key->key_proto != DNS_KEYPROTO_DNSSEC &&
148 key->key_proto != DNS_KEYPROTO_ANY)
149 return (false);
150 return (true);
151}
152
153void
154dst_key_setbits(dst_key_t *key, uint16_t bits) {
155 unsigned int maxbits;
156 REQUIRE(VALID_KEY(key));
157 if (bits != 0) {
158 RUNTIME_CHECK(dst_key_sigsize(key, &maxbits) == ISC_R_SUCCESS);
159 maxbits *= 8;
160 REQUIRE(bits <= maxbits);
161 }
162 key->key_bits = bits;
163}
164
165uint16_t
166dst_key_getbits(const dst_key_t *key) {
167 REQUIRE(VALID_KEY(key));
168 return (key->key_bits);
169}
